@startuml jquku_Matrix-Chatbot

actor User
participant "Matrix Client" as MC
participant "Main Module" as Main
participant "Message Evaluation" as ME
participant "NLP Module" as NLP
participant "Response Management" as RM
database "PostgreSQL DB" as DB
participant "Knowledge Domain Modules" as KDM

User -> MC: Send message
MC -> Main: Receive message event
Main -> NLP: Process message
NLP -> NLP: Apply NLP pipeline
NLP --> Main: Processed message
Main -> ME: Evaluate message
ME -> DB: Query knowledge base
DB --> ME: Return relevant information
ME --> Main: Evaluation results
Main -> RM: Generate response
RM -> DB: Update statistics
DB --> RM: Confirm update
RM --> Main: Formatted response
Main -> MC: Send response
MC -> User: Display response

note right of KDM
  Includes:
  - Index Evaluation
  - Small Talk Evaluation
  - Organisation Evaluation
end note

KDM -> DB: Populate knowledge base
DB --> KDM: Confirm data insertion

@enduml